snippet: Thirteen items related to the career of Whitney Houston drew a total of more than $80,000 on Saturday.
abstract: Thirteen items related to the career of deceased pop singer Whitney Houston sell for a total of more than $80,000 at a Julien’s auction in Beverly Hills, Calif.
lead_paragraph: Thirteen items related to the career of Whitney Houston drew a total of more than $80,000 on Saturday.

headline.main: Whitney Houston Items Are Sold at Auction
